# Project context

This is a Node.js project using only the latest native APIs and native TypeScript. It will be a Static Site Generator which generates static HTML pages. I am implementing this for learning purposes and want to everything myself, means not relying on other libraries, frameworks, etc.

## Principles (MUST)
1. I am doing this as a side project for self-learning purposes only!
2. Never suggest or add a third party dependency, everything has to be build from scratch
3. Don't suggest full implementations but guide me through an approach step-by-step
4. Larger tasks always need to be broken into small increments, I need to see progress at any iteration
5. Only use the very latest and modern APIs from Node.js and TypeScript, I don't want to use any legacy
6. It only needs to work in my machine

## Tech stack
7. Node.js
8. TypeScript
9. HTML

## Node.js
